    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244400/extras/f173d4859cbea03b6fa02f1454d74bb3.avif?t=1719249958\" width=616 height=125 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ready yourself to Pop that Button</strong></h2>Craft a powerful defense and drive back the waves of evil buttons! With an array of turrets, utilities and traps, fight your way through a variety of lush environments - Earn coins and parts with every victory and design your very own button!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244400/extras/caa8106f2d772d2d2e850f0706bb2235.poster.avif?t=1719249958\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244400/extras/caa8106f2d772d2d2e850f0706bb2235.webm?t=1719249958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244400/extras/caa8106f2d772d2d2e850f0706bb2235.mp4?t=1719249958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244400/extras/5eadb996e6ee75127b5fcb66187ccc88.avif?t=1719249958\" width=616 height=125 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be the Button you've always wanted! </h2></strong><br>Earn coins and expand your collection of Hats, Special Effects and Buttons.<br>Survive as long as you can and pop that button at high speeds to unleash coin multipliers! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244400/extras/d1547c1159b9a8b472354fc2f2b13324.poster.avif?t=1719249958\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it