r></li><li>Choose from 3 difficulty options.<br></li><li>In-game Buttonpedia.<br></li><li>10 environments with a variety of terrians and strategies. <br></li><li>10 boss battles.<br></li><li>Accessability options.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244400/extras/2c6cf7860a26e4aa8dd498165f105eda.avif?t=1719249958\" width=616 height=265 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A bit about the Developer</h2></strong><br>Reality Adrift studio is a small independent game studio based in Scotland who strive to<br>produce creatively diverse games that can connect with players around the world.",
